data.description: This stunning five bedroom home sits on the perfect half acre corner lot. Downstairs features the spacious kitchen, living room with fireplace, dining room, breakfast area, one full bathroom and one bedroom. Upstairs, you will find an additional three bedrooms, guest bath and an oversized owners suite! The spectacular backyard is the perfect size for any activities you can think of and it is fully fenced.
